<tr>
<td class="mbox-image">
<div style="width: 52px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ambox_content.png" class="image" title="Ambox content.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/f4/Ambox_content.png" width="40" height="40" border="0" /></a></div>
</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>contains too many minor or trivial fictional references</b>. Mere <a href="/wiki/Trivia" title="Trivia">trivia</a>, or references unimportant to the overall <a href="/wiki/Plot_(narrative)" title="Plot (narrative)">plot</a> of a work of fiction, should be deleted. See also <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:What_Wikipedia_is_not" title="Wikipedia:What Wikipedia is not">what Wikipedia is not</a>. <small><i>(July 2008)</i></small></td>
