on_to_the_United_States" title="Immigration to the United States">Immigration</a> (<a href="/wiki/Mexico_%E2%80%93_United_States_barrier" title="Mexico – United States barrier">Mexico barrier</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Third_Border_Initiative" title="Third Border Initiative">Third Border Initiative</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Obesity_in_the_United_States" title="Obesity in the United States">Obesity</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Racism_in_the_United_States" title="Racism in the United States">Racism</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Same-sex_marriage_in_the_United_States" title="Same-sex marriage in the United States">Same-sex marriage</a></span></div>
